<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="contribute.css">
</head>
<body class="body-contribute-page">
  <div class="contribute-container">
    <p class="contribute-paragraph">
      Seventh Circle thrives because of our amazing community. Whether you're able to <span class="contribute-highlight">donate</span>, 
      <span class="contribute-highlight">volunteer</span>, or join as a <span class="contribute-highlight">member</span>, every bit of support keeps our venue alive and kicking. Here's how you can help:
    </p>

    <h2 class="contribute-section-title">Donate</h2>
    <p class="contribute-paragraph">
      Your donations keep our doors open, our sound system running, and our stage rocking. Every contribution—big or small—helps cover operational costs, upgrade equipment, and make repairs.
    </p>
    <ul class="contribute-list">
      <li class="contribute-list-item">Make a one-time donation</li>
      <li class="contribute-list-item">Set up a monthly contribution</li>
    </ul>
    <a href="#" class="contribute-button contribute-link">Donate Now</a>

    <h2 class="contribute-section-title">Volunteer</h2>
    <p class="contribute-paragraph">
      Want to get involved? Join the Seventh Circle team! Whether you’re running sound, working the door, or helping with cleanup after shows, your time and effort make all the difference.
    </p>
    <ul class="contribute-list">
      <li class="contribute-list-item">Work sound or run the door at shows</li>
      <li class="contribute-list-item">Help with cleanup and maintenance</li>
      <li class="contribute-list-item">Lend your skills for special projects</li>
    </ul>
    <a href="#" class="contribute-button contribute-link">Sign Up to Volunteer</a>

    <h2 class="contribute-section-title">Membership</h2>
    <p class="contribute-paragraph">
      Becoming a member is the best way to support Seventh Circle! For just $5 a year, you not only gain access to all our shows but also help sustain our DIY community space. Membership is vital to keeping this venue alive and ensures we can continue to host amazing shows.
    </p>
    <a href="#" class="contribute-button contribute-link">Join Now for $5</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
